description.desc: Boosts the accuracy and the mastery of your Guns. This skill only applies when you equip a Gun.
description.name: Gun Mastery

description.desc: Attacks multiple monsters by quickly firing a few bullets, so fast that the naked eye can't see the shooting.
description.name: Invisible Shot

description.desc: Attacks a monster by throwing a grenade. The distance the grenade travels depends on how long you press the skill key.
description.name: Grenade

description.desc: Uses parts of HP and MP to temporarily boost the firing speed of the Gun.This skill can only be triggered when the Gun is equipped. \nRequired Skill : #cLevel 5 or above on Gun Mastery
description.name: Gun Booster

description.desc: This skill allows you to pretend shooting a gun, faking out the monsters, and instead of firing bullets, it'll fire a flag. This will temporarily stun up to 2 monsters.
description.name: Blank Shot

description.desc: Allows for a longer, more sustained jump than a regular jump.
description.name: Wings

description.desc: Uses the recoil of the gun to run back after a gunshot. \nRequired Skill : #cLevel 5 or above on Wings#
description.name: Recoil Shot
